verses.roman:
ācāryaratna iṅha, paṇḍita-purandara
gaṅgādāsa paṇḍita iṅha, paṇḍita-śaṅkara

synonyms: ācāryaratna—Candraśekhara; iṅha—here; paṇḍita-purandara—Purandara Paṇḍita; gaṅgādāsa paṇḍita—Gaṅgādāsa Paṇḍita; iṅha—here; paṇḍita-śaṅkara—Śaṅkara Paṇḍita.
translation: "Here are Ācāryaratna, Purandara Paṇḍita, Gaṅgādāsa Paṇḍita and Śaṅkara Paṇḍita.
